Standing in Critter Kingdom with stolen military hardware in the parking lot. Sable helped pick them. Kade felt happy. Asked her to slap him. She refused: "You're not dying. You're just here."
SPARK 4: Standing in the Rain
Outside the apartment, looking up at the window where Mariana and Sofia waited. Understanding that the vault he most wants to crack is the one upstairs. It opens from the inside.
