Driving to Bay 47. Reached for Mariana's hand. "I'm happy, Mariana, surprised and happy. Thank you, Mariana." Not manipulation. Truth.
SPARK 7: Resisting the Locks
Storage facility. Every unit a mystery. The itch screaming. "Don't let me go in these other units, Rigs." Asked for help. Fought it. Won (3 hits exactly on Composure). For them.
SPARK 8: Colorful Blankets
"Maybe we could get blankets to cover everything, some mattresses. What do you think? Some colorful blankets?" The thief trying to make a home for a 10-year-old.
SPARK 9: Marcus's Handshake
"I'm happy to learn how to end confrontations with handshakes." Paid 20k to displace squatters instead of threatening them. Learning.
SPARK 10: "My Family"
